Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:44.31,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 8: Memories\NDraw Spirals of the Past..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the rain's stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of the roka fruit will be\Nweaker after the rain, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done organizing\Nthe documents from Laxdo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.86,0:01:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I do not have much on the\Nprogress during convalescence, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be helped. It's too far to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I don't like this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi! You were only allowed\Nto be away for two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it'd been a while since I'd been\Nout of the castle, so I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what don't you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,People believe she's Zen's fiancée,\Nand everyone's attention is on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Some wonder if they will gain\Nanything from being in her good graces,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and countless others are investigating to\Nsee if another house has fallen from favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Shirayuki to be careful, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She has her job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Obi, I'll have you\Nact as Shirayuki's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a record of threatening her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That part depends on Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I gave you permission\Nto leave the grounds by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think of the possibility\Nthat you wouldn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start from the west side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen you two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Miss Kiki and I have had\Nfun on watch together, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no recollection of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, you knew that this\Nman was one of Zen's attendants?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I met him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The master forgot his own\Nshortcomings and got mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen said he wanted to leave\Nthis man with you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The chief herbalist also said it was okay\Nif that was what the prince wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, she said she would\Naggressively, vigorously,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and thoroughly make the\Nmost use of him she could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can decide to send him away\Nwhenever you want, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep him with you for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, need an introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Obi. I have fake names, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you wearing a mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're harvesting roka fruit, but the\Nsmell they give off makes people drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryu. This person is--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard. It's fine. The prince and chief\Nherbalist both gave their permission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this quickly, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Only pick the ones that have a four-pointed\Nstar pattern at the tip of the fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from the shriveled ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you getting drunk on the smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. As long as this is\Nwhat you mean by a four-pointed star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My hand's moving on its own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to move\Nyour hands, then take these, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll put these in\Nunderground storage now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the jars placed there\Nsix months ago should be ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'll see how those are doing and\Nbring them back to the medicine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This work could try your patience, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? If you\Nkeep doing it, it's interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? As an apprentice court herbalist,\Nand a friend of the prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be having a lot of\Nfun with what you have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a long meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like he's doing his job properly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miss. Do you ever wish\NPrince Zen wasn't a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time you say that,\NI'll take it as an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.01,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, he's amazing... That Prince Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss, please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's roka that has been soaked for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should try drinking it so you\Nknow what it tastes like, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Obi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.42,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,--It burns!\N--It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Herbalist, that's not roka,\Nit's alcohol, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Good job figuring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, you can't hold your liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever wish Prince Zen wasn't a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Lord Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mitsuhide Louen,\Nof the Sereg Knights from the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have him by your side starting from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Prince Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to remain by your side\Nfor the present by Prince Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually wanted to\Nserve my brother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-No, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious from the\Nmoment you were introduced.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you looked at him was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very observant. As expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what am I doing letting him see through me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late. I thought you\Nweren't able to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate my ability to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard you got a new attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have anything to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with\Nsomeone ordered to be by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's uncomfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Must be hard being a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that like it\Nhas nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A humble archer guard like me\Ndoesn't understand hard things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 'cause you're dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a pretty face, so it's fine.\NAnd I'm a good archer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't see the pretty boy\Nin front of you? That's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,--What? Is that your new attendant?\N--Prince Zen! Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sorry. I should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come down later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be bad if people find out the\Nprince is playing with someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, please wait! Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen, was the one who\Njust climbed the tree your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You noticed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have any friends. So don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't interfere--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing more than an attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're with me,\Nthat's all you'll ever be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Prince Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would ask that you not\Nsay cold words like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? C-Cold...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. I'm hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only said what was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:11:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That back that was still young...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about the\Nburden he bore during this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your new attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers are talking about him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's young, and he came suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's a little different\Nfrom a soldier or retainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about him is strange,\Nso it's hard to figure out how to react.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard he's a skilled swordsman, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat him, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.76,0:12:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face shows everything, Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to tell what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who would say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yum! What's in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just snuck into the\Nmess hall and made something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. It really is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good with your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, the time I spend\Nwith you is the most fun and relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of becoming\Na prince's consort, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have no intention of marrying a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.87,0:14:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.41,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be on the night shift from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.54,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be able to walk around during\Nthe day like I have been anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can get\Naway sometimes at night, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate my ability to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri the archer guard.\NHe came to the castle four months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He is about the same age as Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They are probably meeting in secret\Nthinking of each other's social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,From what the soldiers said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,he's a normal boy who came\Nto work here from a far away land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, something bothers me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into him a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you in a daze about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,P-P-Prince Zen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You were like {\i1}that{\i0}.\NThat's why you're like {\i1}this{\i0} now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's cold at night already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, in order to protect myself\Nand my authority as a prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,how much distance do you think I need\Nto put between me and those around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from your perspective,\Nmy brother's good at that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could just copy him,\NI wouldn't have to learn it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ze--\N--No, it's fine. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just wanted to ask myself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,An archer guard boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that it wouldn't be hard\Nto get hired for a position like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he cannot come\Nto the inner areas of the castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,with Prince Zen going out, there is plenty\Nof opportunity for contact between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I have looked into it more,\NI believe we should be wary of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I had you stay by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The position of Zen's personal attendant\Nhas been vacant for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's rebelling\Nagainst being a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy named Atri...\NHe switched to the night shift?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That appears to be the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Atr--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince... Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get those injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't run away\Nor anything, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you his friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys... stop messing around...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you cut me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a problem if you let your feelings\Nget the best of you after we've gotten this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.31,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here with\Nthat kind of half-assed resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you bastards doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The infamous attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We have business with Prince Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to bring him out to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to return\NPrince Zen safely, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a roundabout way to do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He already suspected, I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear your name and business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, why don't you throw\Naway your sword, Prince Izana.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We are what's left of\Nthe Lido family you punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Izana, do you know how many\Npeople who served the Lido family
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,lost their means to earn\Na living because of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how many,\Nbut I know what kind of people they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They were idiots who called\Nthemselves victims, pawns of their lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but lined their own pockets\Nby trampling on the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who think of the citizens\Nof the land before their own profit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,are working hard even now in\Nthe land of Lido for Clarines' sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to them, where were\Nyou useless rebels hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri, we don't need him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill Izana here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.02,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri... You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a Lido rebel, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything to do other\Nthan to rid myself of my resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I understood after I met you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How laughable we were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A warm room, delicious food,\Nfriends who cherished you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The smile you showed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You had all that just because you\Nwere born as royalty in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was ridiculous from\Nthe bottom of my heart, Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you think of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still looking for answers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Da... Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Atri... Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.44,0:21:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That face... is too easy to read...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be... so sad... so seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've been better...\Nif you hadn't been a prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His back, eyes, and heart were still young...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I didn't know anything\Nabout the burden he bore...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And back then, Zen just stifled his cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.19,0:24:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen's always been a prince, and there\Nare people who act because of that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.61,0:24:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, your eyes are a beautiful color...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.15,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.20,0:24:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up somewhere annoying, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:20.15,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 9: Feelings that Connect and Reach"
